data.description: Perfectly located on an attractive cul-de-sac in prestigious north central community. Large mature trees, a forested walking path and community pool, tennis courts & picnic areas. Easy access to highways in all directions. Live gate guard for extra security. The best schools in San Antonio. 4 BR, 4 BA with a flex room that could easily be 5 BRs. 33 ft in-ground "Keith Zars" pool and a large backyard with plentiful grass. Home features a large kitchen with both an island and breakfast bar, plentiful storage throughout, and a beautiful wooden dual staircase. The large master bedroom features an updated bathroom with a 7 ft long dual shower, and walk-in closet with a modular closet system you can arrange to fit your needs. All counters, flooring, kitchen & master bath renovated in 2020. 1st floor BR with private bath. Comes with a home warranty from Choice Home Warranty good through Sep 2024. For VA eligible buyers, the owner's loan is assumable at an incredible 2.25% interest rate!
